<h1>World Sim Game Documentation Change Summary</h1>
<p>Version: Ver0.2.6.b</p>
<p>Baseline: Ver0.2.6.a.</p>
<p>Status: patch release metadata and implementation summary.</p>
<h2>Generated Official Files</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>docs/official/game_universal_documentation_ver0.2.6.b.doc</code></li>
<li><code>docs/official/versions/game_doc_ver0.2.6.b.doc</code></li>
<li><code>docs/official/versions/game_doc_ver0.2.6.b_change_summary.doc</code></li>
</ul>
<h2>Patch Delta</h2>
<ul>
<li>Updated the active version marker to <code>0.2.6.b</code>.</li>
<li>Added the HSV color picker release flow: exact manual apply, cancel safety, auto-avoid preview, and modal pause behavior.</li>
<li>Carried forward the unified shallow/deep water rendering and snapshot fields.</li>
<li>Polished world-generation progress ownership so the central overlay contains the full progress bars and the side panel only shows concise status.</li>
<li>Reduced river visual weight and kept river geometry/cache diagnostics available.</li>
<li>Improved natural-region validation and shape repair diagnostics for strip/sliver regions.</li>
<li>Added map label priority and collision avoidance for country, capital, city, and province labels.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Validation</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>make check-text</code> required for release.</li>
<li><code>git diff --check</code> required for release.</li>
<li><code>make</code> required for release.</li>
<li>Probe checks required where the executable is available and not locked.</li>
</ul>
</body>
